<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <style>
    button {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: black;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    input {
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    input {
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    /* Styling specific to the Mercury Slideshow Gallery page */
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .gallery {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .image-container {
      margin: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .image-container img {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .image-container img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    /* Additional styling for the Mercury page */
    .neptune-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .neptune-image {
      width: 400px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .neptune-facts {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .close {
      opacity: 0;
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      right: 10px;
      font-size: 30px;
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
  </style>
  <title>Neptune</title>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="wrapper">
    <header>
      <h1>Galactic Explorer</h1>
      <nav>
        <button onclick="goBack()">Back</button>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <h1>Neptune</h1>
      <div class="gallery" onclick="openModal()">
        <div class="image-container">
          <img src="/img/planetImg/nep1.jpg" alt="Neptune 1">
        </div>
        <div class="image-container">
          <img src="/img/planetImg/nep2.jpg" alt="Neptune 2">
        </div>
        <div class="image-container">
          <img src="/img/planetImg/nep3.jpg" alt="Neptune 3">
        </div>
  </div>

    <!-- The Modal -->
    <div id="myModal" class="modal">
        <img style="height: 100vh; width: 100vh;" class="modal-content" id="modalImage" />
        <span style="cursor: pointer" id="close" onclick="closeModal()">&times;</span>
      </div>
    <div class="neptune-facts">
      <h3>Facts About Neptune</h3>
      <p>
        Neptune, the eighth planet in our solar system, is a real showstopper with its mesmerizing blue color and wild weather. It's way out there, about 30 times farther from the Sun than Earth. What's really cool is that it tilts a lot on its axis, giving it a unique spin. Winds on Neptune are crazy strong, like, up to 1,500 miles per hour strong â€” the fastest in our whole solar system! The atmosphere is full of interesting clouds, and that deep-blue look? Yeah, that's because of methane hanging around. Inside, it's a mix of water, ammonia, and methane over a rocky core. Neptune's buddy Triton, discovered in 1846, orbits the planet in the opposite direction, which is kind of funky. We got to know Neptune better in 1989 when NASA's Voyager 2 swung by and gave us some awesome insights into this chilly giant.</p>
      <!-- Add more facts as needed -->
    </div>

    <div style="padding-bottom: 1rem;">
      <h4>Credits:</h4>
      <p>These facts are sourced from [NASA]. Visit their website for more information: <a href="https://www.nasa.gov/" target="_blank">[https://www.nasa.gov/]</a></p>
    </div>
    
  </main>
</div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 Galactic Explorer</p>
  </footer>
  
   <script>document.getElementById('myModal').style.display = 'none';</script>
  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
